PACE hires Cowen to explore alternatives . PACE Health Management Systems Inc said it engaged Cowen & Co as its lead investment banker to help the company explore " various alternatives , including debt or equity offerings as well as strategic alliance opportunities . " " We believe that additional capital resources will not only provide funding for growth and development , but will also result in a stronger balance sheet that will reflect the stability prospective customers will be evaluating as the size of our installations increase , " said Roger Huseman , chief financial officer of the healthcare data software firm . ( ( - - Chicago Newsdesk 312 - 408 - 8787 ) ) 
